case_circumstances: This woman was found in an outside storage area of an unfinished apartment building.  She was found on the floor of the storage unit (4' wide, 5' long, 8' in height) fully dressed.  She had placed newspaper on the floor to lay on a small sponge under her head.  No apparent trauma was noted but her body was in severe decomposition. Workers stated they had noticed a foul odor for the last three weeks. No identification was established
